1937;;O.H.M.S.;;British;;Raoul Walsh;;Wallace Ford, John Mills, Anna Lee;;action/comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/O.H.M.S._(film);;An American gangster evades the New York Police's pursuit of him for a murder he didn't commit by fleeing to England with the victim's papers, having assumed his identity. Once in England he joins the British Army and finds romance and adventure on campaign in China.[1]